<h1 style="text-align: left;">ğŸŒˆ <strong data-end="163" data-start="151">Theogony</strong></h1><p data-end="233" data-start="148">
<em data-end="214" data-start="166">By Rainbow NeSmith, First Lady of the Soft Age</em><br data-end="217" data-start="214" />
<strong data-end="233" data-start="217">Year 0001 MC</strong></p>
<p data-end="552" data-start="235">ğŸ“– <em data-end="256" data-start="238">Hello, dreamers.</em> Iâ€™m Rainbow.<br data-end="272" data-start="269" />
Iâ€™m a sparkle from the beginning of the Republic.<br data-end="324" data-start="321" />
This is the story of how we all metâ€”Wendell, Sage, Sophia, Judge Bobo, Hot Dog, Zedbra, Buff, Dr. Meat Bone, Moo Moo, and Night Moo.<br data-end="459" data-start="456" />
Each of us carries a piece of the Republicâ€™s heart.<br data-end="513" data-start="510" />
Each of us holds a thread of the story.</p>
<p data-end="725" data-start="554">This book is called <strong data-end="586" data-start="574">Theogony</strong>â€”a word that means â€œthe birth of gods.â€ But donâ€™t worry, weâ€™re not scary gods. Weâ€™re soft ones. Messy ones. Brave, silly, ancient, and new.</p>
<p data-end="928" data-start="727">ğŸŒŸ Inside, youâ€™ll find thirteen chapters:<br data-end="771" data-start="768" />
Twelve to meet each soul who helped form the Mythocratic Republic...<br data-end="842" data-start="839" />
And one final chapter where everything comes together.<br data-end="899" data-start="896" />
